r than words!\u201d\nCompare the record of American\nworkers with, subsidized coluinnisfs\nin our war effort. The results ob\ntained by men and women war work\ners are the best answer to their crit\n_'.V\nICS.\nf\ni\ni'\n\u2018fy-.lft: -'\u2018FV- Jjv i,-!.\nyr\nF\n\nThe\nExchange Printing Company\n\u25a0W.U\nJob Printing and Publishing\nPrinters of the\n=?3 '1 i \u00a3i\nv;\nSummit County Labor News\n:r' :p- .1\nPublications, Periodicals, Books, Bylaws,\nPrograms, Annual Statements, Hand Bills,\nLetterheads! Statements, Invoices, Circular\nLetters, Business Cards, Envelopes, etc.\nFR-51S5 Give U* a Ring FR-5155\nl\u2019;\n1\nFREE ESTIMATES, REASONABLE PRICES\nNo Job too Large, None Too SmalL\nPROMPT SERVICE.\nV -v I 4\nr j-:\n\nUnion Shop\n\u2022V\u201e, 5\n\u25a0r I I I\ni\nThe\ni\n\u25a0J\n4>\nV\nEXCHANGE PRINTING CO.\n920 S. High Street\n\nAKRON.","height":"27380","width":"21600"}}
